data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This delightful 4-bedroom, 1.5-bath brick ranch is the perfect blend of classic charm  and modern updates. Situated on a generous lot with a large backyard, this property offers both space and style. Need  more space? The garage has been thoughtfully converted, providing an additional living area. This versatile space can be  transformed into a playroom, home gym, or an extra bedroom – the possibilities are endless! Don't miss the chance to  make this charming brick ranch your forever home. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities of  comfortable, stylish living in a prime location!
